<section class="py-14 md:py-20 px-6 md:px-20" style="background: #F5F2EC;">
  <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 md:gap-20 items-center">
      <!-- Left – copy -->
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 reveal-hidden">
        <p class="font-mono-spec text-11 uppercase mb-4" style="color: #C4783A; letter-spacing: 0.2em;">Why Starting Now Matters</p>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-32 md:text-44 font-medium mb-6" style="color: #1C2E23; line-height: 1.1;">
          Every month you wait,<br>the gap widens.
        </h2>
        <div class="font-heading text-16 font-light space-y-4 mb-8" style="color: #4A5550; line-height: 1.8;">
          <p>
            Ancestral microbiome disruption doesn't stabilize. It compounds.
            Every generation loses more of the bacteria that regulated digestion,
            energy, and metabolic health. The bloating gets worse. The fatigue deepens.
            The inflammation spreads. It gets harder to reverse the longer you wait.
          </p>
          <p>
            The traditional foods that maintained your foundational bacterial ecosystem
            aren't coming back. And every generic probiotic on the shelf was designed
            for Western biology — not yours. They don't survive stomach acid. They
            don't feed bacteria after delivery. They don't address the specific
            depletion patterns your heritage carries.
          </p>
          <p>
            That's why we built a new category. Adaptobiotics — the first probiotic
            engineered for the biological tax of modern life. MAKTREK delivers bacteria alive. FOS feeds
            them on arrival. Two capsules a day. No diet changes. Results within weeks.
            That's why people don't cancel.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a href="/products/origin" class="btn btn--primary inline-block">
          Start Feeling Better — $34/mo
        </a>
        <p class="font-mono-spec text-11 mt-4" style="color: #8A9490;">
          Vangay et al., Cell, 2018 — Sonnenburg & Bäckhed, Nature, 2016
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4 mt-1">
          <a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.cell.2018.10.029" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-mono-spec text-11 py-1.5 transition hover:underline" style="color: #C4783A;">
            Vangay et al. →
          </a>
          <a href="https://doi.org/10.1038/nature18846" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-mono-spec text-11 py-1.5 transition hover:underline" style="color: #C4783A;">
            Sonnenburg & Bäckhed →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right – divergence chart -->
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 reveal-hidden">
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12" style="background: #EDE8DF; border: 1px solid #DDD6CC;">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 440 250" class="w-full" style="max-width: 100%;" aria-label="Microbiome divergence chart showing declining diversity across modern populations generations">
            <line x1="50" y1="50" x2="370" y2="50" stroke="rgba(28,46,35,0.08)" stroke-width="1" />
            <line x1="50" y1="100" x2="370" y2="100" stroke="rgba(28,46,35,0.08)" stroke-width="1" />
            <line x1="50" y1="150" x2="370" y2="150" stroke="rgba(28,46,35,0.08)" stroke-width="1" />
            <line x1="50" y1="200" x2="370" y2="200" stroke="rgba(28,46,35,0.08)" stroke-width="1" />

            <!-- Ancestral baseline -->
            <path d="M 60 180 C 120 178, 200 175, 360 170" fill="none" stroke="#1C2E23" stroke-width="2" opacity="0.35" stroke-dasharray="6 4" />
            <text x="365" y="168" fill="#8A9490" font-size="11" font-family="JetBrains Mono, Courier New">Ancestral</text>

            <!-- Diaspora trajectory -->
            <path d="M 60 180 C 120 170, 180 140, 240 110 S 320 60, 360 40" fill="none" stroke="#C4783A" stroke-width="2.5" />
            <text x="365" y="38" fill="#C4783A" font-size="11" font-family="JetBrains Mono, Courier New">Diaspora</text>

            <!-- Divergence gap shading -->
            <path d="M 60 180 C 120 170, 180 140, 240 110 S 320 60, 360 40 L 360 170 C 200 175, 120 178, 60 180 Z" fill="#C4783A" opacity="0.08" />

            <!-- Generation markers -->
            <line x1="110" y1="30" x2="110" y2="220" stroke="rgba(28,46,35,0.10)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 4" />
            <text x="110" y="238" fill="#8A9490" font-size="11" font-family="Jost" text-anchor="middle">Gen 1</text>

            <line x1="210" y1="30" x2="210" y2="220" stroke="rgba(28,46,35,0.10)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 4" />
            <text x="210" y="238" fill="#8A9490" font-size="11" font-family="Jost" text-anchor="middle">Gen 2</text>

            <line x1="310" y1="30" x2="310" y2="220" stroke="rgba(28,46,35,0.10)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 4" />
            <text x="310" y="238" fill="#8A9490" font-size="11" font-family="Jost" text-anchor="middle">Gen 3</text>

            <!-- Y-axis label -->
            <text x="15" y="120" fill="#8A9490" font-size="11" font-family="JetBrains Mono, Courier New" transform="rotate(-90, 15, 120)" text-anchor="middle">
              Microbiome Diversity
            </text>
          </svg>
          <p class="font-mono-spec text-11 text-center mt-4" style="color: #8A9490;">
            Illustrative model based on published environmental shift-microbiome research
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

